{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":800,"text":"Let's go back to 1957."},{"time":6680,"text":"Representatives\nfrom six European countries"},{"time":10720,"text":"had come to Rome"},{"time":12480,"text":"to sign the treaty that was\nto create the European Union."},{"time":17840,"text":"Europe was destroyed."},{"time":20560,"text":"A world war had emerged from Europe."},{"time":25280,"text":"The human suffering was unbelievable"},{"time":27960,"text":"and unprecedented."},{"time":31720,"text":"Those men"},{"time":33720,"text":"wanted to create a peaceful,"},{"time":37880,"text":"democratic Europe,"},{"time":40120,"text":"a Europe that works for its people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43760,"text":"And one of the many building blocks"},{"time":46600,"text":"in that peace project"},{"time":48880,"text":"was a common European market."},{"time":53080,"text":"Already back then,"},{"time":55240,"text":"they saw how markets,"},{"time":57080,"text":"when left to themselves,"},{"time":59440,"text":"can sort of slip into being\njust the private property"},{"time":64519,"text":"of big businesses and cartels,"},{"time":68360,"text":"meeting the needs of some businesses"},{"time":71520,"text":"and not the needs of customers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75840,"text":"So from our very first day,"},{"time":78680,"text":"in 1957,"},{"time":81360,"text":"the European Union had rules"},{"time":84240,"text":"to defend fair competition."},{"time":87680,"text":"And that means competition on the merits,"},{"time":91000,"text":"that you compete\non the quality of your products,"},{"time":94240,"text":"the prices you can offer,"},{"time":96200,"text":"the services, the innovation\nthat you produce."},{"time":100400,"text":"That's competition on the merits."},{"time":103240,"text":"You have a fair chance\nof making it on such a market."},{"time":107320,"text":"And it's my job,"},{"time":109360,"text":"as Commissioner for Competition,"},{"time":112160,"text":"to make sure that companies\nwho do business in Europe"},{"time":115880,"text":"live by those rules."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120360,"text":"But let's take a step back."},{"time":124320,"text":"Why do we need rules\non competition at all?"},{"time":128880,"text":"Why not just let businesses compete?"},{"time":132600,"text":"Isn't that also the best for us"},{"time":135320,"text":"if they compete freely,"},{"time":137640,"text":"since more competition"},{"time":139920,"text":"drives more quality,"},{"time":142120,"text":"lower prices, more innovation?"},{"time":147080,"text":"Well, mostly it is."},{"time":151520,"text":"But the problem is\nthat sometimes, for businesses,"},{"time":156320,"text":"competition can be inconvenient,"},{"time":163120,"text":"because competition means\nthat the race is never over,"},{"time":167760,"text":"the game is never won."},{"time":170400,"text":"No matter how well\nyou were doing in the past,"},{"time":173080,"text":"there's always someone"},{"time":174920,"text":"who are out there\nwanting to take your place."},{"time":180360,"text":"So the temptation to avoid competition"},{"time":183560,"text":"is powerful."},{"time":186320,"text":"It's rooted in motives\nas old as Adam and Eve:"},{"time":191800,"text":"in greed for yet more money,"},{"time":195640,"text":"in fear of losing\nyour position in the market"},{"time":199120,"text":"and all the benefits it brings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203960,"text":"And when greed and fear"},{"time":206920,"text":"are linked to power,"},{"time":208800,"text":"you have a dangerous mix."},{"time":212280,"text":"We see that in political life."},{"time":215360,"text":"In part of the world,"},{"time":217240,"text":"the mix of greed and fear"},{"time":219640,"text":"means that those who get power"},{"time":222280,"text":"become reluctant to give it back."},{"time":228920,"text":"One of the many things"},{"time":230480,"text":"I like and admire in our democracies"},{"time":235240,"text":"are the norms"},{"time":237080,"text":"that make our leaders hand over power"},{"time":240280,"text":"when voters tell them to."},{"time":244720,"text":"And competition rules\ncan do a similar thing in the market,"},{"time":248920,"text":"making sure that greed and fear\ndoesn't overcome fairness."},{"time":255600,"text":"Because those rules mean"},{"time":257160,"text":"that companies cannot misuse their power\nto undermine competition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264040,"text":"Think for a moment about your car."},{"time":268720,"text":"It has thousands of parts,"},{"time":272280,"text":"from the foam that makes the seats"},{"time":275680,"text":"to the electrical wiring\nto the light bulbs."},{"time":279680,"text":"And for many of those parts,"},{"time":282000,"text":"the world's carmakers,"},{"time":283600,"text":"they are dependent\non only a few suppliers."},{"time":289120,"text":"So it's hardly surprising"},{"time":291680,"text":"that it is kind of tempting\nfor those suppliers"},{"time":295760,"text":"to come together and fix prices."},{"time":299920,"text":"But just imagine what that could do"},{"time":301840,"text":"to the final price\nof your new car in the market."},{"time":308520,"text":"Except, it's not imaginary."},{"time":312400,"text":"The European Commission"},{"time":314600,"text":"has dealt with already\nseven different car parts cartels,"},{"time":320480,"text":"and we're still investigating some."},{"time":324320,"text":"Here, the Department of Justice"},{"time":327520,"text":"are also looking\ninto the market for car parts,"},{"time":330920,"text":"and it has called it\nthe biggest criminal investigation"},{"time":334480,"text":"it has ever pursued."},{"time":337320,"text":"But without competition rules,"},{"time":339760,"text":"there would be no investigation,"},{"time":342240,"text":"and there would be nothing\nto stop this collusion from happening"},{"time":346160,"text":"and the prices of your car to go up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351600,"text":"Yet it's not only companies"},{"time":353960,"text":"who can undermine fair competition."},{"time":356960,"text":"Governments can do it, too."},{"time":359720,"text":"And governments do that\nwhen they hand out subsidies"},{"time":363920,"text":"to just the favorite few, the selected."},{"time":369240,"text":"They may do that\nwhen they hand out subsidies --"},{"time":372320,"text":"and, of course,\nall financed by taxpayers --"},{"time":376680,"text":"to companies."},{"time":378760,"text":"That may be in the form\nof special tax treatments,"},{"time":383720,"text":"like the tax benefits"},{"time":385160,"text":"that firms like Fiat,\nStarbucks and Apple got"},{"time":390080,"text":"from some governments in Europe."},{"time":394120,"text":"Those subsidies stop companies\nfrom competing on equal terms."},{"time":399240,"text":"They can mean that\nthe companies that succeed,"},{"time":402840,"text":"well, they are the companies\nthat got the most subsidy,"},{"time":406400,"text":"the ones that are the best-connected,"},{"time":408720,"text":"and not, as it should be,"},{"time":410880,"text":"the companies that serve\nconsumers the best."},{"time":415560,"text":"So there are times when we need to step in"},{"time":418720,"text":"to make sure that competition\nworks the way it should."},{"time":423160,"text":"By doing that, we help\nthe market to work fairly,"},{"time":427720,"text":"because competition gives consumers\nthe power to demand a fair deal."},{"time":433840,"text":"It means that companies know\nthat if they cannot offer good prices"},{"time":438360,"text":"or the service that's expected,"},{"time":440960,"text":"well, the customers\nwill go somewhere else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446680,"text":"And that sort of fairness\nis more important"},{"time":449360,"text":"than we may sometimes realize."},{"time":455560,"text":"Very few people think\nabout politics all the time."},{"time":459600,"text":"Some even skip it at election time."},{"time":463880,"text":"But we are all in the market."},{"time":466400,"text":"Every day, we are in the market."},{"time":470280,"text":"And we don't want businesses\nto agree on prices in the back office."},{"time":475520,"text":"We don't want them\nto divide the market between them."},{"time":479640,"text":"We don't want one big company"},{"time":481560,"text":"just to shut out competitors"},{"time":484240,"text":"from ever showing us what they can do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":488440,"text":"If that happens,"},{"time":490760,"text":"well, obviously, we feel\nthat someone has cheated us,"},{"time":494160,"text":"that we are being ignored\nor taken for granted by the market."},{"time":499680,"text":"And that may undermine\nnot only our trust in the market"},{"time":503280,"text":"but also our trust in the society."},{"time":507680,"text":"In a recent survey,"},{"time":509640,"text":"more than two-thirds of Europeans"},{"time":512080,"text":"said that they had felt\nthe effects of lack of competition:"},{"time":517880,"text":"that the price\nfor electricity was too high,"},{"time":521280,"text":"that the price for the medicines\nthey needed was too high,"},{"time":525560,"text":"that they had no real choice"},{"time":527080,"text":"if they wanted to travel\nby bus or by plane,"},{"time":530440,"text":"or they got poor service\nfrom their internet provider."},{"time":534240,"text":"In short, they found that the market\ndidn't treat them fairly."},{"time":539000,"text":"And that might seem\nlike very small things,"},{"time":544000,"text":"but they can give you this sense"},{"time":547720,"text":"that the world isn't really fair."},{"time":551720,"text":"And they see the market,\nwhich was supposed to serve everyone,"},{"time":556600,"text":"become more like the private property\nof a few powerful companies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":563680,"text":"The market is not the society."},{"time":566080,"text":"Our societies are, of course,\nmuch, much more than the market."},{"time":571720,"text":"But lack of trust in the market"},{"time":574400,"text":"can rub off on society"},{"time":577280,"text":"so we lose trust in our society as well."},{"time":583480,"text":"And it may be the most important\nthing we have, trust."},{"time":589880,"text":"We can trust each other\nif we are treated as equals."},{"time":596080,"text":"If we are all to have the same chances,"},{"time":600520,"text":"well, we all have to follow\nthe same fundamental rules."},{"time":605560,"text":"Of course, some people and some businesses\nare more successful than others,"},{"time":611360,"text":"but we do not trust in a society"},{"time":614000,"text":"if the prizes are handed out"},{"time":616080,"text":"even before the contest begins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":621280,"text":"And this is where\ncompetition rules come in,"},{"time":625160,"text":"because when we make sure\nthat markets work fairly,"},{"time":628680,"text":"then businesses compete on the merits,"},{"time":631920,"text":"and that helps to build the trust\nthat we need as citizens"},{"time":637200,"text":"to feel comfortable and in control,"},{"time":640880,"text":"and the trust that allows\nour society to work."},{"time":646000,"text":"Because without trust,\neverything becomes harder."},{"time":650640,"text":"Just to live our daily lives,\nwe need to trust in strangers,"},{"time":655000,"text":"to trust the banks who keep our money,"},{"time":658800,"text":"the builders who build our home,"},{"time":662200,"text":"the electrician\nwho comes to fix the wiring,"},{"time":665280,"text":"the doctor who treats us when we're ill,"},{"time":667640,"text":"not to mention\nthe other drivers on the road,"},{"time":670480,"text":"and everyone knows that they are crazy."},{"time":674000,"text":"And yet, we have to trust them"},{"time":677120,"text":"to do the right thing."},{"time":680120,"text":"And the thing is\nthat the more our societies grow,"},{"time":684880,"text":"the more important trust becomes"},{"time":687920,"text":"and the harder it is to build."},{"time":691240,"text":"And that is a paradox of modern societies."},{"time":696960,"text":"And this is especially true"},{"time":699320,"text":"when technology changes\nthe way that we interact."},{"time":703840,"text":"Of course, to some degree,\ntechnology can help us"},{"time":706200,"text":"to build trust in one another\nwith ratings systems and other systems"},{"time":710560,"text":"that enable the sharing economy."},{"time":714360,"text":"But technology also creates\ncompletely new challenges"},{"time":718160,"text":"when they ask us\nnot to trust in other people"},{"time":722120,"text":"but to trust in algorithms and computers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":727920,"text":"Of course, we all see\nand share and appreciate"},{"time":731800,"text":"all the good that\nnew technology can do us."},{"time":735800,"text":"It's a lot of good."},{"time":738240,"text":"Autonomous cars can give people\nwith disabilities new independence."},{"time":743400,"text":"It can save us all time,"},{"time":744840,"text":"and it can make a much, much\nbetter use of resources."},{"time":749240,"text":"Algorithms that rely on crunching\nenormous amounts of data"},{"time":754200,"text":"can enable our doctors\nto give us a much better treatment,"},{"time":758280,"text":"and many other things."},{"time":762440,"text":"But no one is going\nto hand over their medical data"},{"time":767720,"text":"or step into a car\nthat's driven by an algorithm"},{"time":771880,"text":"unless they trust the companies\nthat they are dealing with."},{"time":777560,"text":"And that trust isn't always there."},{"time":781240,"text":"Today, for example,\nless than a quarter of Europeans"},{"time":785440,"text":"trust online businesses\nto protect their personal information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":792720,"text":"But what if people knew"},{"time":795440,"text":"that they could rely\non technology companies"},{"time":798800,"text":"to treat them fairly?"},{"time":802280,"text":"What if they knew that those companies"},{"time":804720,"text":"respond to competition\nby trying to do better,"},{"time":809400,"text":"by trying to serve consumers better,"},{"time":813120,"text":"not by using their power"},{"time":815480,"text":"to shut out competitors,"},{"time":817880,"text":"say, by pushing their services"},{"time":820280,"text":"far, far down the list of search results"},{"time":824040,"text":"and promoting themselves?"},{"time":827920,"text":"What if they knew\nthat compliance with the rules"},{"time":832200,"text":"was built into the algorithms by design,"},{"time":837080,"text":"that the algorithm had to go\nto competition rules school"},{"time":840000,"text":"before they were ever allowed to work,"},{"time":844120,"text":"that those algorithms were designed"},{"time":846880,"text":"in a way that meant\nthat they couldn't collude,"},{"time":850520,"text":"that they couldn't form\ntheir own little cartel"},{"time":853560,"text":"in the black box they're working in?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":857480,"text":"Together with regulation,"},{"time":860280,"text":"competition rules can do that."},{"time":863240,"text":"They can help us to make sure"},{"time":865040,"text":"that new technology treats people fairly"},{"time":869680,"text":"and that everyone can compete\non a level playing field."},{"time":874800,"text":"And that can help us build the trust"},{"time":878080,"text":"that we need for real innovation"},{"time":880520,"text":"to flourish"},{"time":881840,"text":"and for societies to develop for citizens."},{"time":887920,"text":"Because trust cannot be imposed."},{"time":891000,"text":"It has to be earned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":894280,"text":"Since the very first days\nof the European Union,"},{"time":898280,"text":"60 years ago,"},{"time":900800,"text":"our competition rules have helped"},{"time":903760,"text":"to build that trust."},{"time":907120,"text":"A lot of things have changed."},{"time":910440,"text":"It's hard to say\nwhat those six representatives"},{"time":913800,"text":"would have made of a smartphone."},{"time":917000,"text":"But in today's world,"},{"time":918640,"text":"as well as in their world,"},{"time":921280,"text":"competition makes the market\nwork for everyone."},{"time":926000,"text":"And that is why I am convinced"},{"time":928280,"text":"that real and fair competition"},{"time":931480,"text":"has a vital role to play"},{"time":933560,"text":"in building the trust we need"},{"time":935760,"text":"to get the best of our societies,"},{"time":940000,"text":"and that starts with enforcing our rules,"},{"time":945000,"text":"actually just to make\nthe market work for everyone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":948840,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":950240,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":955760,"text":"Bruno Giussani: Thank you."},{"time":959360,"text":"Thank you, Commissioner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":960640,"text":"Margrethe Vestager: It was a pleasure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":962520,"text":"BG: I want to ask you two questions."},{"time":964280,"text":"The first one is about data,\nbecause I have the impression"},{"time":967040,"text":"that technology and data are changing\nthe way competition takes place"},{"time":970480,"text":"and the way competition regulation\nis designed and enforced."},{"time":975160,"text":"Can you maybe comment on that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":976840,"text":"MV: Well, yes, it is\ndefinitely challenging us,"},{"time":980200,"text":"because we both have to sharpen our tools"},{"time":983440,"text":"but also to develop new tools."},{"time":986120,"text":"When we were going through\nthe Google responses"},{"time":989000,"text":"to our statement of objection,"},{"time":991760,"text":"we were going through\n5.2 terabytes of data."},{"time":997080,"text":"It's quite a lot."},{"time":999320,"text":"So we had to set up new systems."},{"time":1002640,"text":"We had to figure out how to do this,"},{"time":1005280,"text":"because you cannot work\nthe way you did just a few years ago."},{"time":1009400,"text":"So we are definitely\nsharpening up our working methods."},{"time":1013880,"text":"The other thing is\nthat we try to distinguish"},{"time":1016040,"text":"between different kinds of data,"},{"time":1017760,"text":"because some data is extremely valuable"},{"time":1020360,"text":"and they will form, like,\na barrier to entry in a market."},{"time":1023640,"text":"Other things you can just --\nit loses its value tomorrow."},{"time":1028560,"text":"So we try to make sure"},{"time":1030119,"text":"that we never, ever underestimate the fact"},{"time":1033599,"text":"that data works\nas a currency in the market"},{"time":1037599,"text":"and as an asset that can be\na real barrier for competition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1043560,"text":"BG: Google. You fined them\n2.8 billion euros a few months ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1048119,"text":"MV: No, that was dollars.\nIt's not so strong these days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1050800,"text":"BG: Ah, well, depends on the --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1053360,"text":"Google appealed the case.\nThe case is going to court."},{"time":1055880,"text":"It will last a while."},{"time":1058240,"text":"Earlier, last year, you asked Apple\nto pay 13 billion in back taxes,"},{"time":1063000,"text":"and you have also\ninvestigated other companies,"},{"time":1066160,"text":"including European and Russian companies,"},{"time":1068240,"text":"not only American companies, by far."},{"time":1070360,"text":"Yet the investigations\nagainst the American companies"},{"time":1074680,"text":"are the ones that have attracted\nthe most attention"},{"time":1077120,"text":"and they have also attracted\nsome accusations."},{"time":1080160,"text":"You have been accused, essentially,\nof protectionism, of jealousy,"},{"time":1083320,"text":"or using legislation\nto hit back at American companies"},{"time":1086240,"text":"that have conquered European markets."},{"time":1088560,"text":"\"The Economist\" just this week\non the front page writes,"},{"time":1092040,"text":"\"Vestager Versus The Valley.\""},{"time":1093960,"text":"How do you react to that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1096600,"text":"MV: Well, first of all,\nI take it very seriously,"},{"time":1099840,"text":"because bias has no room\nin law enforcement."},{"time":1106160,"text":"We have to prove our cases\nwith the evidence and the facts"},{"time":1109360,"text":"and the jurisprudence"},{"time":1111400,"text":"in order also to present it to the courts."},{"time":1114760,"text":"The second thing is\nthat Europe is open for business,"},{"time":1118720,"text":"but not for tax evasion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1120480,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1126800,"text":"The thing is that we are changing,"},{"time":1130560,"text":"and for instance,\nwhen I ask my daughters --"},{"time":1132800,"text":"they use Google as well --"},{"time":1134360,"text":"\"Why do you do that?\""},{"time":1135880,"text":"They say, \"Well, because it works.\nIt's a very good product.\""},{"time":1138880,"text":"They would never, ever,\ncome up with the answer,"},{"time":1141360,"text":"\"It's because it's a US product.\""},{"time":1143960,"text":"It's just because it works."},{"time":1145840,"text":"And that is of course how it should be."},{"time":1147920,"text":"But just the same, it is important\nthat someone is looking after to say,"},{"time":1151360,"text":"\"Well, we congratulate you"},{"time":1153720,"text":"while you grow and grow and grow,"},{"time":1156280,"text":"but congratulation stops"},{"time":1158040,"text":"if we find that you're\nmisusing your position"},{"time":1162000,"text":"to harm competitors\nso that they cannot serve consumers.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1166240,"text":"BG: It will be\na fascinating case to follow."},{"time":1168360,"text":"Thank you for coming to TED."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1169760,"text":"MV: It was a pleasure. Thanks a lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1171520,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}